g) Production and market monopolies 
Since the tourism turnover in the Republic of Macedonia is realized and dependent on the elasticity of the domestic tourist demand, the influence of the competition in the business with tourism is great. The legislation in the catering and tourism provides equal treatment of all participants in this business activity, and in that manner it prevents market and marketing monopolies. 
